Attach script with automatic digital camera
extraction. 

1. Install into /etc/hotplug/attach
2. Open the script with your editor and configure it
3. Activate hotplugd: 
   # egrep -q '^hotplugd_flags' /etc/rc.conf.local || echo \
     'hotplugd_flags=""' >> /etc/rc.conf.local
   # hotplugd
4. Plug in your USB devices :-)

-- 
